"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"http://thethefly.com\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1546:\"<div class=\"note inset-right\">\r\n<ul class=\"checkbox\">\r\n	<li>Pre-designed Color Schemes</li>\r\n	<li>Custom Logo Uploader</li>\r\n	<li>Mega Drop-Down Menu</li>\r\n	<li>Menu Image Option</li>\r\n	<li>Both Fixed and Fluid Layouts</li>\r\n	<li>Pre-designed HTML Boxes</li>\r\n	<li>TheThe Fly Plugins Styles</li>\r\n	<li>WP Post Formats Support</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<p align=\"justify\"><strong>TheThe Shot, our second new theme release of 2012, is one part </strong><strong><a href=\"http://gawker.com/\">Gawker</a>, one part film noir, and one part professional photography studio. </strong>Designed with artists, columnists, andphotographersin mind, it\'s a hip, daring theme on a grayscale motif accented with splashes of color that pull readers in as if they\'ve just opened an envelope marked \"Classified.\"</p>\r\n<p align=\"justify\">What eye-popping new toys have we bundled in this time? Glad you asked. In addition to our already-impressive set of pre-designed boxes, widgets, menus, galleries, and banners, we\'ve added a universal 960 px grid layout generator to make sizing your photos, columns, and boxes a snap. Our usual tabs, accordions, and slider plugins are joined by <a href=\"http://shot.demo.thethefly.com/stuff/plugins/sliding-panels/\">sliding panels</a> you can add at will.</p>\r\n<p align=\"justify\">This theme gives your images, news, or products that extra \"Wow\" factor and lets your visitors know they\'ve come to the right place for cool, contemporary ideas. Check out the live demo and imagine your images and content taking off like a Shot.</p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDa