Press theme for your blog or fashion website. Crafted with subtle details and ample white space, this theme offers visitors a smooth, easy browsing experience with no gaudy, distracting design elements.</p>  \r\n\r\n<p align=\"justify\">All of our standard widgets, modules, and plugins can be added almost anywhere within this theme, and you can quickly customize the color scheme, menus layout, and typography (fonts). Dozens of optional pre-designed boxes and widgets ensure your site remains eye-catching while still assuring a comfortable and intuitive browsing experience. Whether you have an established brand or are just starting out, you\'ll be welcoming a flood visitors to your site in no time with our easy-to-understand instructions and extremely responsive customer service.</p>  \r\n\r\n<p align=\"justify\">Check out the <a href=\"http://demo.thethefly.com?theme=flourish\">Live Demo</a> to see how TheTheFlourish can help you draw in visitors who will bookmark your site and visit again and again.</p>\r\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 01 Dec 2011 10:34:17 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"http://thethefly.com\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:9:\"enclosure\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:2:{s:3:\"url\";s:62:\"http://thethefly.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/screenshot.png\";s:4:\"type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:27:\"http://thethefly.com/xmlns/\";a:3:{s:9:\"demo_link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:40:\"http://demo.thethefly.com?theme=flourish\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explici