(76, 1, '2013-03-13 09:34:52', '2013-03-13 09:34:52', '<div class=\"intro-content-wrapper family-resort-living\">\r\n<p class=\"intro-content-body\">At the heart of this exceptional community experience is a selection of luxurious amenities, enriching events and resort offerings available to Golden Oak residents.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"listing-wrapper experience-detail\">\r\n<div class=\"listing\">\r\n<div class=\"listing-image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/disneygoldenoak/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/GO_FamilyResort_Inset_Summerhouse_lifestyle_web_crops_210x140.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"listing-content\">\r\n\r\n<span class=\"listing-title\">Summerhouse: The Community Hub </span>\r\n<p class=\"listing-body\"><i>Now Partially Open </i></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p class=\"listing-body\">The well-appointed Summerhouse, Golden Oak\'s private clubhouse, is the centerpiece of community activities and events as well as home to the Resident Services Team. A hallmark of your resort experience, Summerhouse offers year-round possibilities for your ideal blend of social, leisure and quality time.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p class=\"listing-body\">Residents and their guests have already begun to enjoy some of the key amenities of Summerhouse:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>State-of-the-art fitness facilities with locker rooms</li>\r\n	<li>Private training area and workout studio</li>\r\n	<li>Courtyard, function lawn and outdoor fire pit</li>\r\n	<li>Heated outdoor pool</li>\r\n	<li>Family room with game area</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"listing-body\">Summerhouse will in the future bring even more of its special kind of magic to Golden Oak: casually sophisticated dining, a private lounge and demonstration kitchen for guest chef appearances and tastings, along with a well-rounded program of events throughout the yearsuch as culinary adventures and special themed and seasonal activities for children and adults alike.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"clear-both\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"listing\">\r\n<div class=\"listing-content\">\r\n\r\n<span class=\"listing-title\">Golden Oak Sculpture Program</span>\r\n<p class=\"listing-body\">Golden Oak will be home to a sculpture series featuring outdoor works that celebrate the whimsical spirit of Disney. Drawing inspiration from Walt Disney\'s childhood daydreaming adventures, the planned theme for the Golden Oak sculpture program is \"Under the Dreaming Tree.\"</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"clear-both\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"listing last\">\r\n<div class=\"listing-image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/disneygoldenoak/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/GO_Experience_InPage_Four_Seasons_Final.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"listing-content\">\r\n\r\n<span class=\"listing-title\">Four Seasons Resort <i>Orlando at Walt Disney World Resort </i></span>\r\n<p class=\"listing-body\">Golden Oak will also encompass Four Seasons Resort <i>Orlando at Walt Disney World Resort</i>currently under construction and scheduled to open in 2014. Highlights of this 444-guest- room hotel include:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Tom Fazio-designed golf course</li>\r\n	<li>Superlative restaurants</li>\r\n	<li>Facilities for private events</li>\r\n	<li>Full-service spa</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"clear-both\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"clear-both\"></div>\r\n</div>', 'The Disney Connection', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '22-revision-3', '', '', '2013-03-13 09:34:52', '2013-03-13 09:34:52', '', 22, 'http://localhost/disneygoldenoak/22-revision-3/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
