(1658, 3, '2013-07-09 18:21:30', '2013-07-09 18:21:30', 'Did you know that if you are upside down on yourmortgageand are having issues paying your mortgage on time due to a hardship you dont have to wait until the bank forecloses on you? The government has put together a program to assist those homeowners who are indesperateneed for help. This video is explain what a short sale is and how this could be a huge benefit vs losing your home.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n[KGVID]http://bricrealty.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/What-is-a-Short-Sale.mp4[/KGVID]', 'What is a short sale?', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1657-revision', '', '', '2013-07-09 18:21:30', '2013-07-09 18:21:30', '', 1657, 'http://bricrealty.com/1657-revision/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1660, 3, '2013-07-09 18:24:04', '2013-07-09 18:24:04', 'In Real Estate there are certain sales where lenders require \"Arms Length Transaction\" such as sort sales. This is required to avoid special relationships between the parties involved. Examples of these \"special relationships\" could be relatives, having a side deal or where one party has control of the other. This is done to ensure that all dealing are fair and real such as prices, conditions to the sale, requirements to the transaction etc.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[KGVID]http://bricrealty.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/What-is-an-arms-length-transaction.mp4[/KGVID]', 'What is a \"Arms Length Transaction\"?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'what-is-a-arms-length-transaction', '', '', '2013-07-09 22:19:43', '2013-07-09 22:19:43', '', 0, 'http://bricrealty.com/?p=1660', 0, 'post', '', 0),
