(428, 1, '2013-03-27 02:06:08', '2013-03-27 02:06:08', '<a href=\"http://bricrealty.com/wp-content/gallery/vue/main.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-301\" id=\"homesid\" alt=\"bermuda\" src=\"http://bricrealty.com/wp-content/gallery/vue/main.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"182\" align=\"left\" border=\"2\" /></a>\r\n\r\nWith the serene feel of Tuscan Village Mirabella is your hidden retreat from the hustle and bustle of the world. Located in one of Orlandos prime areas, minutes away from Disney World, Gaylord Palms, Walford Astoria Golf Club, Outlets and Shopping Malls, Mirabella presents to you an incredible opportunity. This spacious 2 bedroom condo is perfect for the investor whom is searching for a tenanted property. <a href=\"http://bricrealty.com/contact/\"><b>\"Contact Us Now\"</b></a> to schedule your preview.\r\n\r\nMirabella is in the center of it all. Everything you need to live an exciting resort lifestyle community. Restaurants, entertainment, downtown Disney, downtown Orlando, art galleries, Dr. Phillips Performing Arts Centre, and all the major attractions are just minutes away. You will love the convenience of living in this gated luxury condominium community.\r\n<div id=\"gallerybg\">[nggallery id=8]</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<iframe src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?q=150 E Robinson St Orlando, FL&amp;t=m&amp;z=&amp;output=embed\" height=\"315\" width=\"560\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe>', 'Mirabella', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'mirabella', '', '', '2013-08-08 23:28:33', '2013-08-08 23:28:33', '', 1475, 'http://bricrealty.com/?page_id=428', 0, 'page', '', 0),
