(457, 1, '2013-03-24 01:08:17', '2013-03-24 01:08:17', '<p class=\"intro-content-body\">Allow us to give you the Bric Realty VIP treatment. Whether you are looking to purchase a new home, wanting to rent, seeking an investment in real estate or looking for someone to manager your property, Bric Realty is your go-to resource.</p>\r\n[wptab name=\'YOUR VIP PASS\']\r\n<div class=\"listing\">\r\n<div class=\"listing-image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i.istockimg.com/file_thumbview_approve/2694005/2/stock-photo-2694005-couple-in-front-of-house.jpg\" width=\"210\" height=\"140\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"listing-content\">Unlike most real estate companies, our real estate consultants will give you the attention you deserve. We will get to know you and learn exactly what you\'re searching for to minimize down time and wasted visits to properties that don\'t match your level of desire. We use satellite imaging, internet conferencing, internal and external affiliate networking and internet marketing strategies to get the results that you are looking for in a fast, productive and in a money saving environment.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"clear-both\"></div>\r\n[/wptab][wptab name=\'WHY US\']\r\n<div class=\"listing\">\r\n<div class=\"listing-image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/wp-content/themes/my_theme/images/PalmsPropertyPics-1.jpg\" width=\"210\" height=\"140\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"listing-content\"><span class=\"listing-title\">What started out as a part time passion to help friends and family members has now grown into a multi-lingual, domestic &amp; international real estate firm. We service clients from all around the world and cater to both local and foreign buyers and investors. We specialize in you, we cater to you, and we commit to doing everything in our power to help you achieve your dreams and goals. We take the work out of real estate in order to create a better experience to our customers.\r\n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"clear-both\"></div>\r\n[/wptab][wptab name=\'MORE CHOICES\']\r\n<div class=\"listing\">\r\n<div class=\"listing-image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i.istockimg.com/file_thumbview_approve/19311448/2/stock-photo-19311448-portrait-family-relaxing-at-home-by-firelight.jpg\" width=\"210\" height=\"140\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"listing-content\">\r\n\r\n<span class=\"listing-title\">We not only provide affordable choices with a variety of different communities, but we providespeciallybuilt units that fits your needs.</span>\r\n<p class=\"listing-body\">Contact us today so we can get you acquainted. We invite you to learn more by arranging a private showing.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"clear-both\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n[/wptab][end_wptabset]', 'Bric Realty Connection', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '22-revision-43', '', '', '2013-03-24 01:08:17', '2013-03-24 01:08:17', '', 22, 'http://bricrealty.com/22-revision-43/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
