(770, 3, '2013-06-05 18:40:45', '2013-06-05 18:40:45', '<div>Todays real estate market is increasingly complicated and fast-paced with more to consider than ever before. When you partner with Bric Realty, you wont have to navigate this challenging process alone.</div>\r\n<div><a href=\"http://bricrealty.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/whitebar.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-554\" alt=\"whitebar\" src=\"http://bricrealty.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/whitebar-300x14.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"14\" /></a></div>\r\n<div class=\"listing\">\r\n<div class=\"listing-image\"><a href=\"http://bricrealty.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/stock-photo-19212878-happy-young-couple-buying-new-house-e1370454184834.jpg&quot;\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-652 alignright\" alt=\"stock-photo-19212878-happy-young-couple-buying-new-house\" src=\"http://bricrealty.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/stock-photo-19212878-happy-young-couple-buying-new-house-e1370454184834.jpg\" width=\"210\" height=\"140\" /></a></div>\r\n<div class=\"listing-content\">Representing one division of Bric Realty multi-faceted real estate business, Bric Realty benefits from the powerful resources afforded by our international network. Bric Realty can help you find communities and properties that suityour lifestyle while connecting you to reputable lenders, home inspectors and renovation specialists.Our real estate professionals are uniquely qualified to help you with:</div>\r\n Assessing your housing needs         Finding your new home\r\n Negotiating a favorable purchase price  Managing all the details involved in the real estate transaction\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"listing-content\"><a href=\"http://bricrealty.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/whitebar-e1370457551274.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-554\" alt=\"whitebar\" src=\"http://bricrealty.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/whitebar-e1370457551274.png\" width=\"210\" height=\"10\" /></a></div>\r\n<div class=\"listing-content\">Bric Realty is here to explain the home buying process from beginning to end and provide everything you need to successfully complete the sale.</div>\r\n<div><a href=\"http://bricrealty.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/whitebar.png\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-554\" alt=\"whitebar\" src=\"http://bricrealty.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/whitebar-300x14.png\" width=\"500\" height=\"14\" /></a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Buy', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '598-revision-93', '', '', '2013-06-05 18:40:45', '2013-06-05 18:40:45', '', 598, 'http://bricrealty.com/598-revision-93/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(771, 3, '2013-06-05 18:57:35', '2013-06-05 18:57:35', '<div>Bric Realty recognizes that selling your home is not just about business. Bric Realty and its affiliated real estate network will represent your property in the manner it deserves with incomparable cross-marketing abilities provided by our global network.</div>\r\n<div><a href=\"http://bricrealty.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/whitebar.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-554\" alt=\"whitebar\" src=\"http://bricrealty.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/whitebar-300x14.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"14\" /></a></div>\r\n<div class=\"listing\">\r\n<div class=\"listing-image\"><a href=\"http://bricrealty.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/stock-photo-14306471-senior-couple-selling-a-home.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-740\" alt=\"stock-photo-14306471-senior-couple-selling-a-home\" src=\"http://bricrealty.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/stock-photo-14306471-senior-couple-selling-a-home-e1370458163958.jpg\" width=\"210\" height=\"140\" /></a></div>\r\n<div class=\"listing-content\">Your home will be targeted to a qualified audience of influential homebuyers and affluent investors through diverse venues and effective marketing approaches.With an exceptional ability to accurately forecast where the market is headed,our intimate relationship with Christies International Real Estates association of brokers,and a commitment to keeping an active pulse on the latest housing statics, consumer demands and marketing trends, Bric Realty can help net you the highest dollar for your property in the shortest amount of time.</div>\r\n<div class=\"listing-content\"></div>\r\n<a href=\"http://bricrealty.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/whitebar-e1370457551274.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-554\" alt=\"whitebar\" src=\"http://bricrealty.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/whitebar-300x14.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"14\" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nOur real estate professionals can market your home