own through annexation.\r\n\r\nThere are a number of notable sites worth visiting in Longwood, including the Bradlee-McIntyre House, the Longwood Hotel and the surviving oldest pond cypress, Lady Liberty.', 'Longwood', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '856-revision-3', '', '', '2013-06-07 09:57:06', '2013-06-07 09:57:06', '', 856, 'http://bricrealty.com/856-revision-3/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
