(1375, 1, '2013-06-19 07:48:08', '2013-06-19 07:48:08', '<div>Allow us to give you the Bric Reatly VIP treatment. Whether youare lookingto Purchase a new home, Rent, seeking an Investment Opportunity orlooking forsomeone to Manage your property, Bric Reatly is your source. <a href=\"http://bricrealty.com/contact/\">\"Contact Us Now\"</a>to get started today.</div>\r\n<div><a href=\"http://bricrealty.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/whitebar.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-554\" alt=\"whitebar\" src=\"http://bricrealty.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/whitebar-300x14.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"14\" /></a></div>\r\n[wptab name=\'YOUR VIP PASS\']\r\n<div class=\"listing\">\r\n<div class=\"listing-image\"><a href=\"http://bricrealty.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/shutterstock_127375112_cropsmall.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-560\" alt=\"shutterstock_127375112_cropsmall\" src=\"http://bricrealty.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/shutterstock_127375112_cropsmall.jpg\" width=\"210\" height=\"140\" /></a></div>\r\n<div class=\"listing-content\">Unlike most Real Estate companies, our consultants will give you the attention you deserve.We will get to know you and learn exactly what you\'re searching for to minimize down time and wasted visits to properties that don\'t match your level of desire. We use satellite imaging, internet conferencing, internal and external affiliate networking and internet marketing strategies to get the results that you are looking for in a fast, productive and money saving environment.<a href=\"http://bricrealty.com/contact/\">\"Contact Us Now\"</a>to get started today.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"clear-both\"></div>\r\n[/wptab][wptab name=\'WHY US\']\r\n<div class=\"listing\">\r\n<div class=\"listing-image\"><a href=\"http://bricrealty.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/shutterstock_83666818_cropsm.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-565\" alt=\"shutterstock_83666818_cropsm\" src=\"http://bricrealty.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/shutterstock_83666818_cropsm.jpg\" width=\"210\" height=\"140\" /></a></div>\r\n<div class=\"listing-content\"><span class=\"listing-title\">What started out as a part time passion to help friends and family members has now grown into a multi-lingual, domestic &amp; international Real Estate firm. We service clients from all around the world and cater to both local and foreign buyers and investors. We specialize in you, we cater to you, and we commit to doing everything in our power to exceed your expectations. Leave it up to us to create a better experience for you.<a href=\"http://bricrealty.com/contact/\">\"Contact Us Now\"</a>to get started today.\r\n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"clear-both\"></div>\r\n[/wptab][wptab name=\'TURNKEY SOLUTIONS\']\r\n<div class=\"listing\">\r\n<div class=\"listing-image\"><a href=\"http://bricrealty.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/shutterstock_97858535_cropsm.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-568\" alt=\"shutterstock_97858535_cropsm\" src=\"http://bricrealty.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/shutterstock_97858535_cropsm.jpg\" width=\"210\" height=\"140\" /></a></div>\r\n<div class=\"listing-content\">\r\n\r\nOver the years we have developed a turnkey Real Estate purchase experience for both our local and international clients. Our services include exclusive <strong>Developer Relationships, Property Management, Experienced Real Estate Attorney/Title services, International Accounting Firms, Domestic and Foreign National Financing Programs, Home Inspection Services, and International Marketing Strategies.</strong> <a href=\"http://bricrealty.com/contact/\">\"Contact Us Now\"</a> to get started today.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"clear-both\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n[/wptab][end_wptabset]', 'feathered Developments', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '22-revision-75', '', '', '2013-06-19 07:48:08', '2013-06-19 07:48:08', '', 22, 'http://bricrealty.com/22-revision-75/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
