(1442, 1, '2013-06-24 03:47:41', '2013-06-24 03:47:41', 'At BRIC, we take great pride in our long-standing relationships with our clients. Years of experience have put us at the top of the industry and our state of the art technology and training ensures that you are getting ultimate value. As not just managers but also investors we know what matters most and the level of attention needed to make your rental business profitable.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWhether you own a single unit or a large portfolio it is our promise to deliver second to none service to you. We use various social media, Internet, referral and print avenues to bring you the best tenants possible for your property. Our in house maintenance staff is trained to minimize expenses while doing the job the right way the first time around.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>\"<a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://bricrealty.com/contact-us/\">Contact Us Now</a>\"</strong> to get started today.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nCurious on how we would handle your account? Below is a snapshot on ways we execute our systems to provide you and your tenants with great service. If you are considering using a Property Manager we would love the opportunity to talk to you.\r\n\r\n<strong>Lease Only Services</strong>\r\n Evaluate and Price Property\r\n Advertise Property\r\n MLS Access\r\n Show Property to Prospective Tenants\r\n Qualify and Screen Tenants\r\n Facilitate Lease Preparation and Signing\r\n\r\nFor Detailed Information please continue reading below.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Property/Tenant Management Services</strong>\r\n Evaluate and Price Property\r\n Advertise Property\r\n MLS Access\r\n Show Property to Prospective Tenants\r\n Qualify and Screen Tenants\r\n Facilitate Lease Preparation and Signing\r\n Hold Security Deposits in Broker Escrow Account\r\n Collect Rent and Pay Monthly Property Maintenance Bills\r\n Accurate Year End Accounting\r\n Set Up Emergency and Non Emergency Repairs\r\n Move in and Move out Walk Through Service with Tenants\r\n\r\nFOR DETAILED INFORMATION PLEASE \"CLICK HERE NOW\".\r\n\r\n<strong>Hiring a Professional Property Manager reduces vacancies and increases income.</strong>\r\n\r\nOur Goal is to find Quality Tenants and Help Maintain Your Investment.\r\n\r\nComply with all Federal, State and Local Laws! <a href=\"http://bricrealty.com/contact-us/\">\"Contact Us Now\"</a> to hire our team to manage your Real Estate investments.\r\n\r\n<b>Tenant Showings</b>- Show prospective tenants vacant units as soon as reasonably possible. Pre-screening process will be conducted via telephone. Maintain a showing schedule and report results to Client. Maintain daily telemarketing efforts for anyone who initially called in. Track tenant lead sources.\r\n\r\n<b>Tenant Screening</b>- Conduct thorough tenant screening to include full background check, credit and criminal check, eviction check (at the district magistrate level) at the Tenant\'s expense. Third party company guarantees accuracy and checks all 50 states at three different levels. One of the most thorough in the industry. Approval depends on points system determined by BRIC. All screening is compliant with fair housing laws.\r\n\r\n<b>Tenant Placement</b>- Place qualified tenants in vacant units as soon as possible to minimize vacancy. Conduct lease signing to educate tenant on the lease terms, collection procedures, systems of the home, emergency procedures, and other key elements of the lease. We will determine rents based on current market value and consult with Client only if outlined in the Agreement.\r\n\r\n<b>Rent Collections</b>- Collect monthly rents from the tenants payable to BRIC, provide receipts for cash payments, and notify owner of any delinquencies with respect to payments of rent. We will serve the proper preliminary notices in the event an eviction is required.\r\n\r\n<b>Advertise Properties</b>- Thoroughly advertise units as an ordinary expense in 25 different places; including the newspaper, internet outlets, referral programs, government programs, and other proprietary media.\r\n\r\n<b>Accounting</b>- Maintain full, detailed and accurate records and accounts of all receipts and expenditures with respect to the property, which records and accounts shall be available for review by the Property Owner or his representatives, at any reasonable time. We will be responsible for the day to day accounting and banking for client.\r\n\r\n<b>Reporting</b>- BRIC has online reporting to all clients. We will send to the Client (Property owner) on or before the fifteenth day of each month, a detailed, itemized statement of all property rent collected and expense receipts incurred during the month.\r\n\r\n<b>Maintenance</b>- We have on call 24-hours per day for maintenance emergencies and will make every reasonable effort to protect the property during emergencies. We will responsible for reducing overall maintenance costs, discovering ways to complete repairs more cost-effectively, and ensure tenant is rebilled for any damages caused by them. We will adhere to maintenance limits set by Client during ordinary monthly maintenance.\r\n\r\n<b>Maintenance Inspections</b>- We, at the request of the Client, will employ the strategy of monthly or quarterly inspections to ensure the well-being of the properties. We will send maintenance personnel through the property and note any repair issues, missing smoke detectors, plumbing and/or mechanical issues. At the time any issues are found we will either remedy (if within the predetermined limits) or notify the Client via email for remedy and/or notify tenant if they are deemed responsible for such repairs.\r\n\r\n<b>Record Management and Backup</b>- It is the goal of the We to keep their systems as paperless as possible. All records are stored electronically with off-site backup to ensure compliance and safeguards against data loss. Records will be made available upon request at any time.', 'Property Management', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '12-revision-42', '', '', '2013-06-24 03:47:41', '2013-06-24 03:47:41', '', 12, 'http://bricrealty.com/12-revision-42/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
