nd Backup</b>- It is the goal of the We to keep their systems as paperless as possible. All records are stored electronically with off-site backup to ensure compliance and safeguards against data loss. Records will be made available upon request at any time.', 'Property Management', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '12-revision-46', '', '', '2013-06-24 03:58:49', '2013-06-24 03:58:49', '', 12, 'http://bricrealty.com/12-revision-46/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
