w a world class sales team while creating an environment of sales\r\n\r\nexcellence second to none. Additionally, Casillas has a passion and expertise for\r\n\r\nupscale residences and million dollar listings.', 'Albert Casillas', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'albert-casillas', '', '', '2013-08-11 04:30:07', '2013-08-11 04:30:07', '', 0, 'http://bricrealty.com/?post_type=agent&#038;p=1966', 4, 'agent', '', 0),
